IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DataDivAdvanced.

DATA DIVISION.
* This is a comment line inside DATA DIVISION
01 EMPLOYEE-RECORD.
   05 EMPLOYEE-NAME  PICTURE IS X(30).
   05 EMPLOYEE-ID    PICTURE IS 9(5).
   05 EMPLOYEE-SALARY PICTURE IS 9(7)V99.
01 COUNTER          PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 FLAG             PICTURE IS A.
01 AMOUNT           LIKE COUNTER.
01 ARRAY-ITEMS      PICTURE IS 9(5) OCCURS 10 TIMES.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY "Done".